(39456, 2, 0, '3... 2... 1...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 39498, 'Captured Goblin to Player'),
(39456, 3, 0, 'Tell my wife I love her very much!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 39499, 'Captured Goblin to Player'),
(39456, 4, 0, 'Um... you do realize there\'s a bottom to this cage?!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 39496, 'Captured Goblin to Player'),
(39456, 5, 0, 'Just open the door... oh no!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 39500, 'Captured Goblin to Player'),
(39582, 0, 0, 'I\'m so money!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19579, 39574, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Thrall'),
(39582, 1, 0, 'No one attacks the Big G and lives!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19565, 47396, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Player'),
(39582, 2, 0, 'Here\'s some of that moolah back that I took from you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19577, 39572, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Thrall'),
(39582, 3, 0, 'I SEE THE TRAITOR IS HERE TO RESCUE YOU, WARCHIEF. HOW CONVENIENT. YOU WILL BOTH BOW TO ME OR FALL TOGETHER!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19567, 39530, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 4, 0, 'I need to move these toxic assets onto a sucker... like you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19570, 39560, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 5, 0, 'Gotta trim some fat around here. I\'m downsizing the company!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19573, 39558, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Ultimate Footbomb Uniform'),
(39582, 6, 0, 'Here, I need to unload some toxic assets!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19568, 39551, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 7, 0, 'I\'m downsizing the cartel, starting with you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 19571, 39556, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Thrall'),
(39582, 8, 0, 'Uncle! Uncle! I give! You guys are too much for me!', 14, 0, 100, 20, 0, 19580, 39542, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 9, 0, 'I\'m beaten. You\'ve shown me the error of my ways. From here on out, I promise to reform the way the cartel is run!', 14, 0, 100, 274, 0, 19581, 39536, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 10, 0, 'I\'m your goblin, Thrall. What would you have of me?', 14, 0, 100, 6, 0, 19582, 39543, 'Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39582, 11, 0, 'It will be as you say! Long live the Bilgewater Cartel! For the Horde!', 14, 0, 100, 15, 0, 19583, 39589, 'Trade Prince Gallywix to Thrall'),
(39594, 0, 0, 'Thrall grunts and thinks a moment on what to do with the Trade Prince.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 39585, 'Thrall to Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39594, 1, 0, 'For now, you will remain the Trade Prince of the Bilgewater Cartel.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 22513, 39586, 'Thrall to Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39594, 2, 0, 'I will send a representative from amongst your people to the new warchief, Garrosh Hellscream in Orgrimmar.', 14, 0, 100, 1, 0, 20148, 39587, 'Thrall to Trade Prince Gallywix'),
(39594, 3, 0, 'You will have a new home in Azshara and the Bilgewater Cartel will become a part of the Horde!', 14, 0, 100, 25, 0, 20149, 39588, 'Thrall to Trade Prince Gallywix');
